Name: Nebuli
About the game: Jump and shoot your way to glory! Nebuli is a fast-paced single-player first person shooter with two modes: Mission and Endless Complete each mission to unlock the next level where you'll encounter new and more challenging Nebuli. You'll pick up powerful guns and power ups to slow down time or clear the Nebuli out of your way as you deliver the bomb to destroy the enemy ship. As you progress, you'll need to conserve your power ups and improve your aim to stay alive. Good luck.
